nh thần cạnh tranh của anh ấy. Nhưng sự cạnh tranh của họ trở nên phức tạp khi họ giành được danh hiệu cao quý \"Song tinh trừ quỷ\"—hai chiến binh tối cao định mệnh kết hôn và sinh ra chiến binh tâm linh tối thượng!</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"66078","season":1,"vote_average":8.435,"vote_count":360},"modified":"2023-06-19T17:03:12.000Z","cast":["Hanae Natsuki","Megumi Han","Junichi Suwabe","Murase Ayumu","Ishikawa Kaito","Kohsuke Toriumi","Masaya Takatsuka","Misako Tomioka","Kiyono Yasuno","Jun Fukuyama"],"director":[],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Hanae Natsuki","name_vi":"Hanae Natsuki","name_original":"Natsuki Hanae","tmdb_id":1256603,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/alTb0DlcPIbcwM08WSmxFai58sd.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1256603"},{"name":"Megumi Han","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Megumi Han","tmdb_id":1164931,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cwnwrPg1YvB19TbfouC4ShGPmbQ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1164931"},{"name":"Junichi Suwabe","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Junichi Suwabe","tmdb_id":9721,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4S7c3n3r07A83HvkLrnWZGVhiHg.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/9721"},{"name":"Murase Ayumu","name_vi":"Murase Ayumu","name_original":"Ayumu Murase","tmdb_id":1325230,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3aGM6KpcCIEKOXP9510tzaKc8uw.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1325230"},{"name":"Ishikawa Kaito","name_vi":"Ishikawa Kaito","name_original":"Kaito Ishikawa","tmdb_id":1324666,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fzjIkotjUHHs3wgftM9tqdsG8ph.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1324666"},{"name":"Kohsuke Toriumi","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Kohsuke Toriumi","tmdb_id":122647,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vlRQ77taCCKh7itCZn3IWJUiYQr.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/122647"},{"name":"Masaya Takatsuka","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Masaya Takatsuka","tmdb_id":1243481,"profile":"h